data.description: Welcome home. The 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is nestled under mature trees, has a covered porch that extends the front of the home, and a carport. The open faced cabinets in the kitchen, abundant counter space, and views overlooking the pond will win your heart. A large bonus room is just off the front porch--a 4th bedroom, game room, storage, or craft room would be excellent options. The RV Carport measures 35'x20' and has septic and electrical hookups. Just off the lovely back patio is a pond that is stocked with cat fish, hybrid blue gill, and regular perch. The raised bed gardens are ready for your green thumb. Beyond the home is a horse barn with 5 stalls and is cross fenced with a riding pen. The tack room is 12'x13'. The front of the property includes mature live oaks and walking/riding trails but just beyond the tree line are 5 +/- acres of cleared pasture that would be perfect for grazing, building, or recreation.
